OL,6,FThe father of a man who was killed by
OL,7,Fa drink-drug driver says he will never
OL,8,Fforgive the man who left his son to
OL,9,Fdie.
OL,11,FKieran Andrews, 26, was a passenger in
OL,12,Fa car travelling at high speed towards
OL,13,Ftowards in in March last year.
OL,15,FAs the car approached the village, at
OL,16,Faround 10:30am, the driver mounted the
OL,17,Fpavement and crashed through a section
OL,18,Fof fencing.
