OL,6,FKieran was left with horrific injuries
OL,7,Fand, despite strangers trying to help
OL,8,Fhim, he was pronounced dead by
OL,9,Femergency services at the scene.
OL,11,FAnother passenger who was sitting in
OL,12,Fthe back of the car was also injured
OL,13,Fin the collision.
OL,15,FThe driver, Luke Sullivan, 24, fled
OL,16,Fthe scene and hid in for hours after
OL,17,Fto avoid police.
OL,19,F"As a father, I had to break it to my
OL,20,Fdaughters and his younger brother",
OL,21,Fsays Kierans dad, John Andrews.
