OL,3,CFather will never forgive drink-drug
OL,4,Cdriver who left son to die
OL,6,F"As a father, I couldn't protect him
OL,7,Fbut we protected them all when they
OL,8,Fwere growing up and they never come to
OL,9,Fno harm, then someone has gone and
OL,10,Ftook his life like that."
OL,12,FFollowing the collision, Sullivan was
OL,13,Farrested on suspicion of causing death
OL,14,Fby dangerous driving and failing to
OL,15,Fstop following a collision. He was
OL,16,Flater released on bail.
OL,18,FAt on Wednesday (29 May), Sullivan was
OL,19,Fsentenced to 6 years and 8 months in
OL,20,Fjail. On his release he will be banned
OL,21,Ffrom driving for 5 years.
